snippet.title: I Flipped 100 Rocks in a Rainforest, Here's What I Found...
snippet.description:
New merch released! https://terragreenstore.com/

Under every rock you flip there's a chance you'll find some sort of life you would have never known was there. And in this video I flew out to Puerto Rico to explore the exotic rainforests! I found all sorts of lizards, spiders, and even snakes. Watch to the end to see the coolest and rarest animals!

If I used any of your copyrighted material in the video and you are not okay with it, please contact me on my business email found in my channel's description so we can reach an agreement.

Thanks for watching and please subscribe!

#animals #rainforest #rock

snippet.description:
Submit a banger video idea here: https://forms.gle/GXK3uwLSuGKPEJzc9

To see what I do behind the scenes or outside my videos, follow me on Instagram

üì∏ Channel Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/tdbricks_/
üì∏ Personal Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/tylerhartlauer/
üì±Tik Tok: tiktok.com/@td_the_creator
‚úâÔ∏è Email for business reasons: td.brickz@gmail.com

Credits:
Non copyright music from Epidemic Sound: https://share.epidemicsound.com/c3oiyn
Outro song from NBHD Nick: https://linktr.ee/nbhdnick 
Background beats from Bakkstab: https://soundcloud.com/realbakkstab
Background beats: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=43MQ4Bfhrlw
Lil Tecca inspired AI song by Torns: https://open.spotify.com/artist/2xnJVU1K87J1Mxi95MWqgK?si=tECJ002rQDO92AmW10w8fg
Netflix inspired outro by Kevin Guinn
Background beats by @xRyBeatzCEOx¬†
Outro by @Keshen8 

Frequently asked questions:
Where do I get my Lego?
- Bricklink.com, Lego Store
How do I make my videos?
- To edit, I use Final Cut Pro X. To film, I use a Canon EOS R8 and my iPhone. To record my voice, I use a RODE VideoMic Go.
Do I have instructions for my Lego builds?
- I sadly don‚Äôt
What do I do with my Lego builds after a video is finished?
- I usually have to take them apart to use for the next Lego build I make

snippet.description:

LYRICS
I check the doors, check the windows, and pull the blinds,
I check the clock, wondering what he‚Äôll pull this time,
I have a feeling that necromancer‚Äôs outside,
And I‚Äôm just trying to stay quiet.

I don‚Äôt sleep much, that's crazy, how‚Äôd you know that?
Keep myself up, that's maybe how you know that,
Promises and contracts I used to keep,
I don‚Äôt sleep much, that's crazy, how‚Äôd you know that?
Keep myself up, that‚Äôs maybe how you know that,
My hallucination I used to see.

Wake up and I find out, did a change up,
Wait ‚Äî Did it change up?
Is it light out yet?
Better find out. Bet,
Imma walk around the edge of the room,
And the bed where I hide my face,
Pace around,
Better try to breathe,
Pace around, Pace around.

(Sleep I found)
I wanna get out there,
But I don‚Äôt try,
I wanna get out there,
But I don‚Äôt try.

I used to see,
It felt so real,
But now I plead,
Just take the deal,
I promised you,
A contract.

snippet.title: Superman | Tickets on Sale Now
snippet.description:
On July 11, the entire world will look up. Get tickets now for #Superman - Only In Theaters and @IMAX 

‚ÄúSuperman,‚Äù DC Studios‚Äô first feature film to hit the big screen, is set to soar into theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures.  In his signature style, James Gunn takes on the original superhero in the newly imagined DC universe with a singular blend of epic action, humor and heart, delivering a Superman who‚Äôs driven by compassion and an inherent belief in the goodness of humankind. 

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and Gunn are producing the film, which Gunn directs from his own screenplay, based on characters from DC, Superman created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.

The film stars David Corenswet (‚ÄúTwisters,‚Äù ‚ÄúHollywood‚Äù) in the dual role of Superman/Clark Kent, Rachel Brosnahan (‚ÄúThe Marvelous Mrs. Maisel‚Äù) as Lois Lane and Nicholas Hoult (the ‚ÄúX-Men‚Äù movies, ‚ÄúJuror #2‚Äù) as Lex Luthor.  The film also stars Edi Gathegi (‚ÄúFor All Mankind‚Äù), Anthony Carrigan (‚ÄúBarry,‚Äù ‚ÄúGotham‚Äù), Nathan Fillion (the ‚ÄúGuardians of the Galaxy‚Äù films, ‚ÄúThe Suicide Squad‚Äù), Isabela Merced (‚ÄúAlien Romulus‚Äù), Skyler Gisondo (‚ÄúLicorice Pizza,‚Äù ‚ÄúBooksmart‚Äù), Sara Sampaio (‚ÄúAt Midnight‚Äù), Mar√≠a Gabriela de Far√≠a (‚ÄúThe Moodys‚Äù), Wendell Pierce (‚ÄúSelma,‚Äù ‚ÄúTom Clancy‚Äôs Jack Ryan‚Äù), Alan Tudyk (‚ÄúAndor‚Äù), Pruitt Taylor Vince (‚ÄúBird Box‚Äù) and Neva Howell (‚ÄúGreedy People‚Äù).

‚ÄúSuperman‚Äù is executive produced by Nikolas Korda, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars Winther.  Behind the camera, Gunn is joined by frequent collaborators, including director of photography Henry Braham, production designer Beth Mickle, costume designer Judianna Makovsky and composer John Murphy, along with composer David Fleming (‚ÄúThe Last of Us‚Äù) and editors William Hoy (‚ÄúThe Batman‚Äù) and Craig Alpert (‚ÄúDeadpool 2,‚Äù ‚ÄúBlue Beetle‚Äù).  

DC Studios Presents a Troll Court Entertainment/The Safran Company Production, A James Gunn Film, ‚ÄúSuperman,‚Äù which will be in theaters and IMAX¬Æ nationwide on July 11, 2025, and internationally beginning 9 July 2025, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

For live streaming of the U.S. Open and the U.S. Women's Open Presented by Ally, plus live scoring, articles, photos and more, visit usopen.com, uswomensopen.com, and the USGA App.

It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). snippet.title: I Tried the Top 50 Airbnbs in America - Day 2
snippet.description:
hello new mexico!!!
donate here - https://www.stjude.org/50states



Wheel of Doom penalties:
1. Running on fumes - You must drive until the tank says ‚Äúempty.‚Äù
2. Local Legend - You must share a meal with a local from the nearest town before moving on.
3. Route Roulette - You must receive directions from a stranger and follow them word for word.
4. Reverse Card - You must turn around the way you came and find another way to your next Airbnb.
5. Detour - You are not allowed to drive on highways to the next Airbnb.
6. Silent Treatment ‚Äì No talking between Ryan & Haley for the entire road trip.
7. Airplane Mode - You must get to your next Airbnb without your phones.
8. Locked Out - You are not allowed to sleep in your next Airbnb.
9. The Split - One of you must split up and find another way to your next Airbnb.
10. Red Light, Green Light - Roll a dice ‚Äî whatever it lands on, you must wait that many hours before hitting the road.
11. Golden Ticket - Congratulations! You have unlocked immunity for 24 hours. It can be activated at any time.

snippet.title: I Built a Giant LEGO Railway for my Pets!
snippet.description:
#ad To celebrate World Play Day 2025, I partnered with The  @LEGO Group to create the ultimate LEGO railway adventure #LEGOWorldPlayDay #LEGOPartner

I Built a Giant LEGO Railway for my Pets! My LEGO train travels through HUGE mountains, glow-in-the-dark and LED lit tunnels and down an insane DIY pool-noodle spiral coaster. But will the train make it or will this end in a complete disaster? 

‚ô° Get the merch: https://aquariuminfo.com/ (worldwide shipping üåé)

SUBSCRIBE for a chance at the ecosystem kit
‚ñ∫  https://www.youtube.com/c/AquariumInfo?sub_confirmation=1

Meet The Crew!
üêà Nori
üê≤ Gizmo
ü¶Ä Noodle & Pickle
ü¶û Mochi
üê¢ Harry 
ü¶ê Ralph
üê∏ Frito & Burrito
ü¶é Lucy & Lemon
üê† Peanut & Jelly
ü¶é Lime & Pepper & Squeak
ü™¶ R.I.P. Kirby

Watch as we build an insane 200ft LEGO railway through the studio, passing by some of your favorite animals, including Ralph my Peacock Mantis Shrimp, Mochi, my grocery store lobster, and the beloved duo Lucy and Lemon, my axolotls. We even build my kitten Nori a rube goldberg contraption to feed him treats when the train passes by! In this adventure-filled episode, we also travel to an abandoned railway to learn about trains in the real world! 

This LEGO train trip will have 5 epic stops, including a dual greenhouse filled with live plants and LEGO botanicals, a snowy mountain featuring miniature Christmas trees and LEGO Santa, a cat cafe, a glow-in-the-dark tunnel with glowing crystals and an arid desert ecosystem with LEGO animals and real cacti. The LEGO train will be equipped with a tiny camera so you can see what the train sees, so be on the lookout for all of the hidden LEGO builds along the way! Can you spot them all?

Watch until the end to see if the train makes it through the entire trip in one piece! This video is perfect for anyone who loves LEGO trains, building custom LEGO builds, axolotls, exotic pets, rare animals, DIY projects or is just interested in what it takes to build an epic DIY LEGO railway! 

If you have any comments, suggestions or questions for this LEGO train video or future videos, leave them down in the comments! Also for additional content like this, video tutorials, project sneak peeks and more, follow me on Instagram @aquariuminfo.

#ad Per celebrare la Giornata Mondiale del Gioco 2025, ho collaborato con The @LEGO Group per creare l'avventura ferroviaria LEGO definitiva #LEGOWorldPlayDay #LEGOPartner

Ho costruito una ferrovia LEGO gigante per i miei animali! Il mio treno LEGO attraversa montagne ENORMI, tunnel fosforescenti e illuminati a LED e scende lungo un folle ottovolante a spirale fai da te con tubi galleggianti. Ma il treno ce la far√† o finir√† in un disastro totale?

‚ô° Acquista il merchandising: https://aquariuminfo.com/ (spedizioni in tutto il mondo üåé)

Guardateci costruire una folle ferrovia LEGO di 60 metri attraverso lo studio, passando accanto ad alcuni dei vostri animali preferiti, tra cui Ralph, la mia Canocchia Pavone, Mochi, la mia aragosta del supermercato, e l'amatissimo duo Lucy e Limone, i miei axolotl. Costruiamo persino un marchingegno Rube Goldberg per dargli dei dolcetti quando passa il treno! In questo episodio pieno di avventure, visitiamo anche una ferrovia abbandonata per imparare a conoscere i treni nel mondo reale!

Questo viaggio in treno LEGO prevede 5 tappe epiche, tra cui una doppia serra piena di piante vive e piante botaniche LEGO, una montagna innevata con alberi di Natale in miniatura e Babbo Natale LEGO, un bar per gatti, un tunnel luminescente con cristalli luminosi e un ecosistema desertico arido con animali LEGO e veri cactus. Il treno LEGO sar√† dotato di una minuscola telecamera per permettervi di vedere ci√≤ che vede il treno, quindi tenete gli occhi aperti per tutte le costruzioni LEGO nascoste lungo il percorso! Riuscite a individuarle tutte?

Guardate fino alla fine per vedere se il treno riesce a percorrere l'intero viaggio intatto! Questo video √® perfetto per chiunque ami i treni LEGO, costruire costruzioni LEGO personalizzate, axolotl, animali esotici, animali rari, progetti fai da te o sia semplicemente interessato a ci√≤ che serve per costruire una ferrovia LEGO fai da te epica!

Se avete commenti, suggerimenti o domande per questo video sul treno LEGO o per i video futuri, lasciateli nei commenti! Per contenuti aggiuntivi come questo, tutorial video, anteprime di progetti e altro ancora, seguitemi su Instagram @aquariuminfo.

Se stai leggendo questo, sei un Super Fan!
Commenta "Cat Cafe" cos√¨ ti noto üêà‚òïÔ∏è

snippet.title: Wiz Khalifa: Tiny Desk Concert
snippet.description:
This Black Music Month, Tiny Desk honors the anniversaries of landmark albums that have shaped the course of music and culture.

Bobby Carter | June 10, 2025
Wiz Khalifa‚Äôs Kush & Orange Juice came out 15 years ago. To honor the anniversary, the Pittsburgh emcee assembled a group of Tiny Desk veterans, Pennsylvania natives and his DJ to reimagine highlights from the classic mixtape, plus tracks from Kush & Orange Juice 2, its similar, yet more mature follow-up.

Something was happening during the entire show and lots of us in the room could feel it. We were waiting for him to engage with us, but he didn‚Äôt. I stepped in after a few songs to remind him that it was OK to do so ‚Äî still, nothing. But then, after ‚ÄúCrime Bud and Women,‚Äù Wiz spoke to the audience for the first and only time, wiping away tears: ‚ÄúYou made me cry. F*** y‚Äôall!‚Äù 

I can muster up a few guesses as to why the emotion overflowed. Wiz had a host of family and friends present in this very intimate setting, including his father. And he did tell me how much he loves performing. But honestly, this sonic masterpiece was good enough to hit the tear ducts. 

SET LIST
‚ÄúRed Eye‚Äù 
‚ÄúMezmorized‚Äù 
‚ÄúThe Kid Frankie‚Äù 
‚ÄúNever Been‚Äù
‚ÄúUp‚Äù
‚ÄúCrime Bud and Women‚Äù 

MUSICIANS
Wiz Khalifa: vocals
Kenneth Wright: music director, bass
DJ Bonics: turntables
Uncle Bubz: keys
Russell Gelman-Sheehan: guitar
Kendall Lewis: drums

TINY DESK TEAM
Producer: Bobby Carter

localized.title: Wiz Khalifa: Tiny Desk Concert
localized.description:
This Black Music Month, Tiny Desk honors the anniversaries of landmark albums that have shaped the course of music and culture.

Bobby Carter | June 10, 2025
Wiz Khalifa‚Äôs Kush & Orange Juice came out 15 years ago. To honor the anniversary, the Pittsburgh emcee assembled a group of Tiny Desk veterans, Pennsylvania natives and his DJ to reimagine highlights from the classic mixtape, plus tracks from Kush & Orange Juice 2, its similar, yet more mature follow-up.

Something was happening during the entire show and lots of us in the room could feel it. We were waiting for him to engage with us, but he didn‚Äôt. I stepped in after a few songs to remind him that it was OK to do so ‚Äî still, nothing. But then, after ‚ÄúCrime Bud and Women,‚Äù Wiz spoke to the audience for the first and only time, wiping away tears: ‚ÄúYou made me cry. F*** y‚Äôall!‚Äù 

I can muster up a few guesses as to why the emotion overflowed. Wiz had a host of family and friends present in this very intimate setting, including his father. And he did tell me how much he loves performing. But honestly, this sonic masterpiece was good enough to hit the tear ducts. 

SET LIST

‚ÄúMezmorized‚Äù 
‚ÄúThe Kid Frankie‚Äù 
‚ÄúNever Been‚Äù
‚ÄúUp‚Äù
‚ÄúCrime Bud and Women‚Äù 

MUSICIANS

snippet.title: EMOTIONAL INTERVIEW ‚Äì Behind the scenes of our flooded desert escape
snippet.description:
4WDs RECOVERED AFTER 82 DAYS & emotional interview ‚Äì Behind the scenes of our flooded desert escape. By now you‚Äôve seen our wild escape from the Simpson Desert floods - but there‚Äôs plenty you didn‚Äôt see‚Ä¶ ü´£

If you did actually miss the eps, check them out here:
Ep 1: https://youtu.be/816Z-XpB0_s
Ep 2: https://youtu.be/_32oDuTWIPI

While we were stuck in Birdsville, we sat down with the crew at the Birdsville Pub for a behind-the-scenes chat to spill everything the cameras missed. Grab a beer and tune in! üçª

Help support Aussie farmers doing it tough üëâüèª https://aussiehelpers.org.au/

Shaun, Graham, Jock, & Jesse - formerly known as 4WD Action - have been delivering the best off-road content in Australia for 20+ years. From epic car builds & 4x4 tips to exploring iconic spots like Fraser Island, Utah, The Kimberley, Colorado, The Rubicon Trail & The Simpson Desert, we create content for every off-roader. We've even hit the tracks with the legends from Donut Media! Whether you‚Äôre rocking a fully modified Toyota LandCruiser or just getting started with your Hilux or Ranger, we‚Äôve got you covered for all things 4WD and adventure.

snippet.title: Los Angeles police chief speaks about National Guard, Marine response to immigration protests
snippet.description:

snippet.title: 2025 U.S. Open Highlights: Round 1, Condensed
snippet.description:

For live streaming of the U.S. Open and the U.S. Women's Open Presented by Ally, plus live scoring, articles, photos and more, visit usopen.com, uswomensopen.com, and the USGA App.

The USGA is a mission-based golf organization whose purpose is to unify the golf community through handicapping and grassroots programs; to showcase the game‚Äôs best talent through the U.S. Open, U.S. Women‚Äôs Open and 13 other national championships and our museum; to provide unbiased global governance with The R&A through the playing, equipment and Amateur Status rules; and to advance issues important to golf‚Äôs future, with a focus on driving sustainability, accessibility and inclusion. As a nonprofit association, our work and our team are driven to act for the good of the game. For more, visit www.usga.org.

snippet.title: Los Angeles protests against ICE immigration raids continue; U.S. Marines, National Guard deployed
snippet.description:
More National Guard troops and hundreds of Marines have been deployed to Los Angeles as violent protests continued for another night, with more than 100 arrests Monday.

California Gov. Gavin Newsom continued to denounce sending the military into the city, filing an emergency motion to block the Marines' deployment. The National Guard has been protecting a federal complex in LA where some immigrants are being held after ICE raids around the city.

The year is 2035 and the world is on the brink of chaos, ravaged by violent conflict and psychological warfare following the events of Black Ops 2 and Black Ops 6. snippet.title: I Tried To Make Something In America (The Smarter Scrubber Experiment) - Smarter Every Day 308
snippet.description:
Get a Smarter Scrubber Here: http://smarterscrubber.com
Interested in Wholesale, or helping us tell the story? Here's a link:
https://forms.gle/XFrLTa5b8kxSvPnu8

I would like to thank the Patrons of Smarter Every Day. They knew about this project early and helped make it happen.
http://www.patreon.com/smartereveryday

John is a great Dad and a good dude. Check out JJGeorge here:
https://www.jjgeorgestore.com/

Our goal is to make these things 100% in America. We're going to have to build some machines in order to do this.
Your support is appreciated.

Mantle's 3D Printing for injection molds is a technology I'm very excited to explore. 
A huge thanks to Ted for participating!
Here's a video on what they do: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uywWr6-nHF4

A HUGE thanks to our Injection Molder Chris Robson, with tons of work from Jeremy:
http://www.robsonco.com/

T&C Metal Stamping (Ask to speak to Weston and tell him Destin sent you!)
https://www.tandcstamping.com/

Search Engine Podcast: 
Episode "The Puzzle of the All-American BBQ Scrubber"
https://www.searchengine.show/the-puzzle-of-the-all-american-bbq-scrubber/

Check out Jeremy Fielding's Channel
https://www.youtube.com/@Jeremy_Fielding

Check out Tim Cook's comments on China at the Fortune Global Forum:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_ng8xQ-SNGc

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
GET SMARTER SECTION

I recommend learning about the Bretton Woods Accords
https://www.federalreservehistory.org/essays/bretton-woods-created

Read about the Bretton Woods system
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bretton_Woods_system

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Smarter Every Day on Patreon
http://www.patreon.com/smartereveryday

Ambiance, audio and musicy things by: Gordon McGladdery 
https://www.ashellinthepit.com/
http://ashellinthepit.bandcamp.com/

Warm Regards,

Destin

snippet.title: ROG Xbox Ally World Premiere Reveal Trailer | Xbox Games Showcase
snippet.description:
Meet the ROG Xbox Ally and ROG Xbox Ally X. Coming this holiday 2025.

Introducing the ROG Xbox Ally and ROG Xbox Ally X ‚Äì two new premium handhelds that combine the power of Xbox with the freedom of Windows 11. This holiday, players can discover another way to play as we combine the power of Xbox with the freedom you expect from Windows 11, created together with ASUS. And this is only the beginning.

‚Ä¢ROG Xbox Ally: powered by the AMD Ryzen‚Ñ¢ Z2 A Processor - balancing performance and power consumption to maximize battery life without sacrificing gameplay quality - 16GB of RAM and 512GB of SSD storage.
‚Ä¢ROG Xbox Ally X: features the AMD Ryzen‚Ñ¢ AI Z2 Extreme processor - allowing us to bring new experiences to life including greater frames-per-second, sharp visuals and increased intelligence - double the storage to have more native games at your fingertips, and 24GB of high-speed RAM and 1TB of SSD storage.

snippet.title: LAPD chief speaks out about deployment of military forces to anti-ICE protests
snippet.description:
Los Angeles Police Department Chief Jim McDonnell and Los Angeles Mayor Karen Bass held a joint news conference Monday on the deployment of military forces to the city as protests over immigration raids continued. "I see two parallel tracks that don't work together, if you will," McDonnell said.

snippet.title: Velcro Suit Mini Games w/Pierson!
snippet.description:
Welcome to the first week of Camp CrunchLabs! This week the nephews return to challenge their favorite uncle! It's not too late to join Camp CrunchLabs! Join here: http://www.campcrunchlabs.com 

Check out Disney's Elio, only in theaters June 20: https://movies.disney.com/elio
#Elio

Each build-it-yourself STEM toy teaches the magic and fun in engineering principles and coincides with exclusive weekly videos like this one that accelerate your learning! Ready for Camp? Visit http://www.campcrunchlabs.com for  more info.

A big thanks to our special guest @pierson for joining me on mercury!

This weeks Challenge:
CREATE SOMETHING AWESOME USING FORCED PERSPECTIVE!
Just like my buddy Zach King or all the photos you see of people at the Leaning Tower of Pisa, use forced perspective to create something awesome!!! Maybe you are driving a shoe as a car, scaling a mountain that is really the floor or creating huge items from household items the sky is the limit!

HOW TO SUBMIT YOUR CHALLENGES?
Parents: Tag challenge project video submissions @crunchlabs with #CampCrunchlabsContest on Instagram, X, TikTok or Facebook. Then complete this form https://www.crunchlabs.com/pages/camp-planet-page-mercury

Open to legal residents of the 50 U.S. & D.C., who are 18+ and the parent or legal guardian of at least (1) child between 8-16 years of age. Grand Prize winner must travel 7/20/25-7/22/25. See Official Rules for full details including entry periods, entry requirements, prize descriptions and judging criteria. Void where prohibited.

Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation.
